{"TopicId":149290,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"\u0026quot;There\u0026#039;s no easy way to say this.\u0026quot;","CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-04T22:09:03Z","PageNum":18,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Andem","CreatedById":155578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-05T23:28:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222789514\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149290\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475710027\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably right about here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThough TBH I didn\u0027t really expect it to go much different. People are mad and confused, along varying ranges of reasonableness. If anything I\u0027m surprised the whole thing has been so civil.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022background:rgb(255,255,255);padding:30px;width:480px;color:rgb(82,82,82);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022font-size:16px;line-height:20px;margin-left:80px;\u0022\u003E\nYou are only allowed to give 25 likes per day. You cannot give any more likes today.\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cul style=\u0022clear:both;width:420px;padding:0px;list-style:none;margin:25px 0px 0px;text-align:right;\u0022\u003E\u003Cli style=\u0022margin-right:5px;float:right;margin-left:10px;\u0022\u003E\nOK\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Norcalplanner","CreatedById":112223,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-05T23:45:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn looking at the job ads through the link at the top of the forum, every job description requires that the applicant speak Spanish fluently. Could the\u00A0language issue\u00A0be a contributing factor to the exodus?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HoloYolo","CreatedById":138353,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-05T23:47:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222789549\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149290\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475711120\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022112223\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Norcalplanner\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Norcalplanner said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn looking at the job ads through the link at the top of the forum, every job description requires that the applicant speak Spanish fluently. Could the\u00A0language issue\u00A0be a contributing factor to the exodus?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould be. I think \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/119307-nightingale/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022119307\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/119307-nightingale/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@nightingale\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0is British, not sure about the other 7 but that could be a problem.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"regex","CreatedById":70807,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-05T23:47:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222789549\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149290\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475711120\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022112223\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Norcalplanner\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Norcalplanner said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn looking at the job ads through the link at the top of the forum, every job description requires that the applicant speak Spanish fluently. Could the\u00A0language issue\u00A0be a contributing factor to the exodus?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso the fact that most of those people are outside of Mexico. Doesn\u0027t explain Roverdude but I know nothing of his spoken language skills. Same for Nightingale.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ThatGuyWithALongUsername","CreatedById":140817,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-05T23:47:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t blame the developers for leaving, they have a good reason, but 1.3 isn\u0027t looking very good with only 10 developers including only\u00A02.5 programmers.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile the idea of 1.2 or 1.3 being the\u00A0LAST update is kind\u00A0of a worst-case scenario, it is entirely possible. Plausible, even.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBACKUP YOUR GAMES, FOR\u00A0THE END IS NEAR!\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:0.0:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_shocked.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:0.0:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kiwi1960","CreatedById":81697,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-05T23:51:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222789351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149290\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475703306\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022143451\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OldLost\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 hours ago, OldLost said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDefine \u0022here\u0022. By \u0022here\u0022 one could infer\u00A0you are also working for Squad.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh good God.... \u0022here\u0022 as in the KSP community... the nit picking is getting out of control. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheKosanianMethod","CreatedById":163034,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-05T23:52:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m trying to fit this thread to the grief model, but I can\u0027t. Someone else wanna do it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RoverDude","CreatedById":105198,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-05T23:53:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222789556\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149290\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475711274\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022708