i said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNIGHTINGGALE IS A VAMPIRE.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/PXrAnbpROvY?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T01:02:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222789514\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149290\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475710027\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf anything I\u0027m surprised the whole thing has been so civil.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMost of the time the KSP community is pretty great. \u00A0It\u0027s why it avoids my ban on reading comments on the internet. \u00A0Typically, that behavior is bad for your health.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"smotheredrun","CreatedById":165894,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T01:13:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat reddit thread needs a good Mod lock out on it. \u00A0Nice that here everyone is more or less friendly, if a bit overly insistent on things (see\u00A0\u0022is \u0027x\u0027 mod updated yet?\u0022 on any mod thread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs for why 8 people left at the same time? \u00A0Just be patient, Douglas Adams, and we\u0027ll find out eventually, one day, years from now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso tell your Kerbals to pack their towels, there is still much to see/explode.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mycroft","CreatedById":158484,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T01:53:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo here, I attempted to separate fact from rumor in this sticky situation. Please read it, and tell me if I got anything wrong, or if you have a fact or a rumor you heard that I didn\u0027t cover.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/149361-what-facts-do-we-know-about-the-devs-leaving/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it\u0027s time we figure out what\u0027s really going on here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T02:01:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mycroft","CreatedById":158484,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T02:04:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222789701\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149290\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475719280\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105624\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pthigrivi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Pthigrivi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027d rather be confused? I think it\u0027s best to alleviate confusion and nip harmful rumors in the bud.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T02:09:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just don\u0027t see what could possibly be achieved by that. We\u0027re not going to know, and its not really our business anyway. Either 1.3 will have fancy new features or it wont, they\u0027ll hire a bunch of cool new devs or they wont, its just not really our business what\u0027s happening personally between any of them. That\u0027s their deal and they\u0027re all adults and they can figure it out.\u00A0Im really happy 1.2 is so great and I\u0027m hugely grateful to everyone who worked so hard on it, those that are staying and those that are moving on alike.\u00A0I really hope Arsonide and Nathan and Claw and all those guys find kickass new work out there. They\u0027re crazy talented and Im sure they\u0027ll do well. I guess I just don\u0027t see how\u00A0some weird citizens inquiry is going to help matters.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-10-06T02:10:28Z\u0022 title=\u002210/06/2016 02:10  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 6, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Pthigrivi\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mycroft","CreatedById":158484,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T02:10:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222789714\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149290\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475719769\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105624\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pthigrivi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Pthigrivi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just don\u0027t see what could possibly be achieved by that. We\u0027re not going to know, and its not really our business anyway. Either 1.3 will have fancy new features or it wont, they\u0027ll hire a bunch of cool new devs or they wont, its just not really our business what\u0027s happening personally between any of them. That\u0027s their deal and they\u0027re all adults and they can figure it out.\u00A0Im really happy 1.2 is so great and I\u0027m hugely grateful to everyone who worked so hard on it. I really hope Arsonide and Nathan and Claw and all those guys find kickass new work out there. They\u0027re crazy talented and Im sure they\u0027ll do well. I guess I just don\u0027t see how\u00A0some weird citizens inquiry is going to help matters.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease do read my post and tell me what I list as facts that we don\u0027t know for sure. I would love to hear that!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T02:13:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI guess I just don\u0027t care that much? I love the game and Im sad so many folks are leaving but it seems weird to get all\u00A0up in their business about it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mycroft","CreatedById":158484,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T02:20:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222789719\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149290\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475720025\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105624\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pthigrivi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Pthigrivi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI guess I just don\u0027t care that much? I love the game and Im sad so many folks are leaving but it seems weird to get all\u00A0up in their business about it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s fine! People are gonna do that if something they don\u0027t like happens.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T02:26:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s odd,\u00A0man. I mean the thing is none of us were there so none of us has any clue what happened. Its kind of silly guess at it. Either way there\u0027s nothing we\u0027re going to say or discover on this message board thats going to change matters. People left on their own terms and next month they\u0027ll be writing great code for someone else. Its just really not the end of the world.\u00A0I just don\u0027t see what possible good from come of it? Teach someone a lesson? When we have no idea what we\u0027re talking about? How? And to what end?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-10-06T02:29:26Z\u0022 title=\u002210/06/2016 02:29  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 6, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Pthigrivi\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nerfclasher","CreatedById":158707,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-06T02:50:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222789733\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149290\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475720785\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105624\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pthigrivi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 minutes ago, Pthigrivi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s odd,\u00A0man. I mean the thing is none of us were there so none of us has any clue what happened. Its kind of silly guess at it. Either way there\u0027s nothing we\u0027re going to say or discover on this message board thats going to change matters. People left on their own terms and next month they\u0027ll be writing great code for someone else. Its just really not the end of the world.\u00A0I just don\u0027t see what possible good from come of it? Teach someone a lesson? When we have no idea what we\u0027re talking about? How? And to what end?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0It\u0027s very sad that this had to happen\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}